Q1:
Welcome to our study! Thank you for your interest in taking part in our experiment.
 

 In this experiment we will ask you to do one questionnaire and three tasks that will evaluate your face processing abilities. In this order, you will do the following tasks:



	Demographics questionnaire: you will need to answer some questions about yourself (1-2 minutes).
	Holistic processing: you will be asked to identify the gender of a set of faces. (10-15 minutes).
	Autism Questionnaire: you will be asked to report your agreement/disagreement with a series of statements (5-10mins).
	Cambridge Face Memory Test: you will be asked to memorize faces (10 minutes).


 

 

You will get specific instructions before the beginning of each task. Please don't take long breaks between each of the tasks.
